> [#IRE](https://twitter.com/hashtag/IRE?src=hash) players observe a moment's
> silence in memory of victims who lost their lives to the attack on Sardar
> Daud Khan hospital. [#Kabul](https://twitter.com/hashtag/Kabul?src=hash)
